# Sunday Coffee Ride

A relaxed 60-minute spin. Keep the effort conversational — if you can't chat, you're going too hard. Focus on smooth pedaling and enjoy the ride. This is active recovery done right.

- 5:00 40%
  - :30 Easy start — let the legs wake up
  - 2:00 Find a comfortable cadence around 85-90rpm
  - 1:30 No pressure today, just turn the pedals
- 15:00 55% 85rpm
  - :30 Settle into a steady rhythm
  - 7:00 Check in — breathing should be relaxed and easy
  - 5:00 Halfway through this block, keep it smooth
- 5:00 50%
  - :30 Ease off slightly
  - 3:00 Enjoy the scenery
- 15:00 58% 90rpm
  - :30 Pick it up just a touch
  - 7:00 Keep that cadence nice and even
  - 5:00 You're doing great — this is what recovery looks like
- 5:00 50%
  - :30 Another easy stretch
- 10:00 55% 85rpm
  - :30 Last steady block
  - 5:00 Almost done — soak it in
- 5:00 40%
  - :30 Cool it down
  - 3:00 Great ride — see you at the coffee shop
